{
  "stem": "22750.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not with permit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were stealing for yourself if you had a mind and you had something, valuable things.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not with permit-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With permit, nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing from the house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything we belong was not to you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Didn't belong to you, like to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of histories we know, and not because I'm saying now, but this is-- I tell you, we thought, in that time, in our little ghetto, maybe they will avoid us a little bit longer because we filled out every befiehl, they call in German, the orders, an order.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the officers-- a couple were around the city, German- were satisfied.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We thought so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's why they will keep us longer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Matter of fact, there was rumors by the name-- he was an officer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was good, a German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The name was Schneider.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he left for a month for vacation to his home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was not from the city, an officer from the army, from the SS.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he had a human feeling, more than the other ones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I call [INAUDIBLE] judgment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he left for a month for a vacation, like what we call here vacation, to his home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were afraid, as now they would come and kill us because he was the one that we thought, in our minds, not only in my mind.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he is the one that-- he keeps us alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was the scare, and this was the way of thinking, and this was life-- as no hope for tomorrow to be alive because they are killed there and killed there when they took them away from our city.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- you always have some connections.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
